      • getBounds

        public static Rect getBounds(Rect pIn,
                             int pCenterX,
                             int pCenterY,

        Rough computation of the smaller Rect that contains a rotated Rect Emulating Canvas.getClipBounds(Rect) after a canvas rotation The code is supposed to be exactly the same as the RectL version, except for int/long The code is written to run as fast as possible because it's constantly used when drawing markers
